  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unpatterned Cut is a addictive action-reflex game you have never experienced before. Push your limits as you slash your enemies, surrounded by a futuristic environment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                           <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316430/extras/6eaf78b1c2e0a9209f1091462c708988.poster.avif?t=1767485558\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316430/extras/6eaf78b1c2e0a9209f1091462c708988.webm?t=1767485558\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316430/extras/6eaf78b1c2e0a9209f1091462c708988.mp4?t=1767485558\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Episodes Logic</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you not bored of repetitive rhythm-reflex games? You no longer need to memorize patterns to complete levels. Unpatterned Cut offers you a unique experience with a different pattern in each retry even at the same level.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >              <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316430/extras/068859f8cc46935dda300f4c5af0ba9b.poster.avif?t=1767485558\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316430/extras/068859f8cc46935dda300f4c5af0ba9b.webm?t=1767485558\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316430/extras/068859f8cc46935dda300f4c5af0ba9b.mp4?t=1767485558\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Chapters</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are 5 chapters and 16 levels in total. Each chapter has features that are different from the previous chapter. For example, if you successfully pass the first chapter, in the second chapter, there will be spawns of enemies with armor that you need to break their armor to be able to cut them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                                <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316430/extras/bcf4b4499114dbad38a84272f8ffa70b.poster.avif?t=1767485558\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316430/extras/bcf4b4499114dbad38a84272f8ffa70b.webm?t=1767485558\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316430/extras/bcf4b4499114dbad38a84272f8ffa70b.mp4?t=1767485558\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Story Mode</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There is a short story mode where you must make choices and explain why you are in the simulation. <strong>You do not have to play the story mode to play the levels.</strong></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unpatterned Cut is a addictive action-reflex game you have never experienced before. Push your limits as you slash your enemies, surrounded by a futuristic environment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                           <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316430/extras/6eaf78b1c2e0a9209f1091462c708988.poster.avif?t=1767485558\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316430/extras/6eaf78b1c2e0a9209f1091462c708988.webm?t=1767485558\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316430/extras/6eaf78b1c2e0a9209f1091462c708988.mp4?t=1767485558\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Episodes Logic</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you not bored of repetitive rhythm-reflex games? You no longer need to memorize patterns to complete levels. Unpatterned Cut offers you a unique experience with a different pattern in each retry even at the same level.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >              <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316430/extras/068859f8cc46935dda300f4c5af0ba9b.poster.avif?t=1767485558\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316430/extras/068859f8cc46935dda300f4c5af0ba9b.webm?t=1767485558\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316430/extras/068859f8cc46935dda300f4c5af0ba9b.mp4?t=1767485558\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Chapters</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are 5 chapters and 16 levels in total. Each chapter has features that are different from the previous chapter. For example, if you successfully pass the first chapter, in the second chapter, there will be spawns of enemies with armor that you need to break their armor to be able to cut them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                                <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316430/extras/bcf4b4499114dbad38a84272f8ffa70b.poster.avif?t=1767485558\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316430/extras/bcf4b4499114dbad38a84272f8ffa70b.webm?t=1767485558\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316430/extras/bcf4b4499114dbad38a84272f8ffa70b.mp4?t=1767485558\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Story Mode</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There is a short story mode where you must make choices and explain why you are in the simulation. <strong>You do not have to play the story mode to play the levels.</strong></p>",
